@startuml
title Use Case B - Keyword Search Flow
skinparam shadowing false

start
:BusinessSystem\ncall POST search;
:SearchRecAPI\nquery, top_k, preferred_tags;
:Clamp **top_k** to [1, 100]\n(default SEARCHREC_DEFAULT_TOP_K);
:Candidate **budget** = top_k ×\nSEARCHREC_SEARCH_CANDIDATE_MULTIPLIER\n(clamped 1..20);
:IndexAdapter.search(query, budget)\n**lexical recall**;
note right
  **Memory:** full scan + cosine on TF
  **OpenSearch:** multi_match title/content/tags
  **DbIndexAdapter:** query terms → **doc_term**\nunion → cosine vs doc.lexical_norm_sq
end note
:VectorAdapter.search(query, budget)\n**recall**;
if (SEARCHREC_MERGE_VECTOR_CANDIDATES?) then (yes)
  :For vector hits not in lexical set:\nIndexAdapter.get_document(id)\nappend row (lexical_score = 0);
else (no)
  :Use lexical rows only;
endif
:For each candidate row:\nFeatureStoreAdapter\nget_doc_features(doc_id);
:Resolve **score_boost**:\nfeature store if present,\nelse index row **score_boost**;
:SearchRecService fusion +\nsort:\n(0.65×lexical + 0.2×vector_blend\n+ tag_score + 0.05×popularity)\n× score_boost\n(vector_blend = min(1, vector_score/5));
:Truncate to **top_k**;
:Return **items** + **total_hits**;
stop
@enduml
